vsParam:
Hey, guys!
I have something to consult you.
What can be used for free assignment?

"Free assignment"...?
Er, is it related to wizardry?

Yes. That's the assignment my grandmother gave me,
I have to submit a report to her regularly.

Grandmother... The most powerful witch you
mentioned before?

That's right. Although I am in another world,
I always sense that I'll get scolded if I become slack.

Although there's no limitation regarding the contents,
it has to be something which honors the name of witches.

"Something honoring the name of witches"...
That's hard to find...

Yes... The first thing comes to mind when speaking of
witches is entering a contract with powerful elves!
That'll be the best if we can pull it off...
Is there anything like the king of elves in this world?
Does the king of fairies count?
We have the king of human.

The Fairy King wouldn't sign a contract with me even if I
strike it down, huh? That's not the king I want...

Er... Are you listening to me? What are you up to
by entering a contract with a human king...

You are right...
I never heard of the "King of Elves".

But I heard about one place that the
elves frequently visit.

Really!? Such a place is real!
Maybe the King of Elves is there too!

Take me there, please!
Hurry up, let's go!

Ah!? Wait, wait a minute, Wilbell!
There's nothing I can do with her!
So this should be the place where the elves gather...

Wow! Monster-shaped elf!
No, elf-shaped monster? It's looking at us!?

Oh, it wants to attack us!
Be careful, guys!

Hee hee, that's what I want!
Alright, bring it on!
Phew... We finally drive it away!

Okay. Let's search for the King of Elves!
King of Elves, King of Elves...

This place has neither strong magical power,
no abnormal mana...
You should change to another assignment.

No. Don't waste our time and energy to search again.
I couldn't feel any strong magical power near here.
Sigh... So is that how it ends...

Wilbell... I understand how you feel,
but you'd better come down to earth and start small, right?

Hmm. I still want to do things that could
make me famous overnight.

It's the fastest shortcut
for grandmother to approve of me...

I bet your grandmother wants to see your growth,
and even the pettiest achievement is accumulation...

I made many attempts, but I couldn't realize perfection.
That's why I wish to make more direct results...

Ah, this world is different from yours, right? Why don't you
find an assignment that can only be done here?

... Right, that's it! This is another world, there must be
something that can knock my grandmother's socks off!

Oh, bucked up so soon...
That's Wilbell.

Ho-ho. Being able to walk of the shadows
is one of her strengths.
